And in doing so, he gives validation and voice to all the witnesses, researchers, doctors, military personnel,

37
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:27,000
and ordinary people who have been attacked, dismissed, and ridiculed over this subject for decades.

38
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:32,000
And he provides shelter and safe haven to those who haven't come out yet.

39
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:36,000
Believing that a phenomenon like this exists, of course.

40
