It's where it came from, why it was here, and what it means for the future of science, society, defense,

42
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:51,000
and where humanity stands in the universe.

43
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:56,000
So with that, enjoy this historic conversation with Aldo Ribello,

44
