79
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,000
You're a long career.

80
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:31,000
But the reason that I am here, as you know, I focus on kind of anomalous phenomena, the nature of reality, is that you tweeted something very interesting.

81
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:35,000
You said as former defense minister, I am provoked to speak on the subject.

82
